title: You need help publishing you little bitch?
description: These cmds allow you to post msgs to the server.

fields.name: corn?channels
fields.value: Get a list of all channel_ids you can post to.

fields.name: corn?publish [channel_id]
fields.value:
Publish the current msg to the channel_id. Requires confirmation.
Ex: corn?publish 13

fields.name: corn?speak [channel_id] [message]
fields.value:
Sends a normal discord message to the specified chanel. Requires confirmation.
Ex: corn?speak 69 united we bargain, divided we beg

fields.name: corn?roles
fields.value: Get a list of all roles you can ping.

fields.name: corn?ping [role_name] [channel_id]
fields.value:
Ping a role and publish the current embedded msg.
Ex: corn?ping twitter 35

fields.name: corn?set [event_name] [optional:msg]
fields.value:
Set the current msg to send when an event is triggered. Use corn?help attributes for a list of events and fillable fields
 Ex: corn?set boost-embed
 corn?set boost-msg Thank you {uname}!!
